<p><a name="eberhart">[1]</a> Eberhart, R. C. and Kennedy, J. (1995). A new optimizer using particle swarm theory. In Proceedings of the sixth international symposium on micro machine and human science, volume 1, pages 39–43. New York, NY.</p>

